WEBVTT

00:01:58.688 --> 00:02:00.625
in the hope that it would all unravel.

00:02:01.697 --> 00:02:03.434
Why go through all that trouble?

00:02:04.358 --> 00:02:06.799
Well, maybe counterfeiting
is a victimless crime?

00:02:07.365 --> 00:02:09.475
These big companies,
they make enough money,

00:02:09.499 --> 00:02:10.770
so if anything,

00:02:10.794 --> 00:02:13.530
counterfeiting is just a free form
of advertising, right?

00:02:14.170 --> 00:02:16.546
And consumers believe just that --

00:02:16.570 --> 00:02:19.467
that the buying and selling of fakes
is not that big a deal.

00:02:20.110 --> 00:02:23.149
But I'm here to tell you
that that is just not true.

00:02:24.848 --> 00:02:28.777
What the tourist on holiday doesn't see
about those fake handbags

00:02:28.801 --> 00:02:31.237
is they may well
have been stitched together